702138f-a.title: Bronx: Lane Avenue - Westchester Avenue
702138f-a.text:
14 to 32 Westchester Square (Lane Ave.), north side, east from
its point of junction with Westchester Ave., to its point of junction
with East Tremont Ave. The vantage point is Westchester Ave. under-
neath the elevated structure of the I.R.T. Pelham Bay Park subway
line.
August 25, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
